{"tid":813150,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新沙士重臨】南韓(港人旅遊熱點)22人被隔離 英女遊客發燒喉痛檢查屬陰性","createTime":"2018-09-10T08:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T09:17:04.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3bbee21cf0e1223c590dfd88e68b62ba77b1a683","tid":813150,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180910/58664154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F58664154&d=QdAYs1uv84AQAC4BClgFMG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=6c33810e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F58664154&h=22230292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180910/58664154</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓繼2015年以來再次發現中東呼吸綜合症(MERS，又稱新沙士)確診病例，目前有22人被隔離，一名與患者同機的英國女遊客出現發燒、咳嗽、咽喉疼痛等病徵，幸檢查後證實屬陰性。<br />\n該名24歲英國女遊客與患者搭乘阿聯酋航空編號EK322航班入境南韓，出現咳嗽、喉痛、暈眩、發燒等症狀，目前在國立中央醫療院的隔離病房接受治療。醫院今早發佈化驗結果，指她的檢查結果為陰性，並表示「將進行第二輪檢查」。<br />\n至於確診感染MERS的61歲南韓男性，目前在國立首爾大學附屬醫院隔離治療，與他有過密切接觸的22人目前正被隔離。由於MERS病毒的潛伏期為2至14天，隔離人士的潛伏期將在本月21日結束。<br />\n南韓政府已將MERS預警級別從第四級的「關心」，提高到第三級的「注意」，並在中央和地方政府設立對策本部，全力防止疫情擴散。"},{"pid":"988ab76a61c96efd5155717af59b1f17ea80c926","tid":813150,"uid":51076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"外國，唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def3da78a20b550185c713ab3f9dcede88d78768","tid":813150,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"988ab76a61c96efd5155717af59b1f17ea80c926","tid":813150,"uid":51076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"外國，唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T08:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b032e3918e19391f25ca7a7ffc88ce4b661c16","tid":813150,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T09:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買樓機會到了"}]}